Don't assign a variable to itself.

## Details

[#](#details)

DON'T assign a variable to itself. Usually this is a mistake.

BAD:

dart

```
class C {
  int x;
​
  C(int x) {
    x = x;
  }
}
```

content_copy

GOOD:

dart

```
class C {
  int x;
​
  C(int x) : x = x;
}
```

content_copy

GOOD:

dart

```
class C {
  int x;
​
  C(int x) {
    this.x = x;
  }
}
```

content_copy

BAD:

dart

```
class C {
  int _x = 5;
​
  int get x => _x;
​
  set x(int x) {
    _x = x;
    _customUpdateLogic();
  }
​
  void _customUpdateLogic() {
    print('updated');
  }
​
  void example() {
    x = x;
  }
}
```

